characters.title: Justicar Enforcer
characters.name: Zwei Lanzer
characters.quote: Call me when you need a miracle
characters.lore: A fallen paladin once devoted to the Church of Nirvanis. He was cast out for questioning the Churchs values and now seeks redemption on his own terms. He joined the Guild Vagabonds with the goal of reforming the guild into an instrument of true order, a disciplined arm of justice that hunts the wicked without political constraints.

combatSkills.name: Cleave
combatSkills.description: A large downward slash that splits the earth.

combatSkills.name: Oathbinder
combatSkills.description: A holy burst of light strikes the ground in front of him.

characters.observations: Has a scar across his left eye. Often lost in thought. Drinks black coffee exclusively.

characters.title: Priestess of the Holy Blade
characters.name: Rei Shirasaki
characters.quote: Let this radiant light purge all that is unholy!
characters.lore: A human Priestess sent by the Church of Nirvannis to join Guild Vagabonds. She is on a mission to banish the Lord of Darkness, who was reported to be unsealed from his tomb after 100 years. She was trained in the art of Holy Weapon, a dangerous skill that can easily sever undeads and demons at the cost of rapidly siphoning life energy to power its blade. Despite having this power, she has a small stature and is very timid, quick to run or mentally shut down if things dont go as planned.

combatSkills.name: Smite
combatSkills.description: A blast of holy energy strikes in front of Rei. Strong against demons and undead.

combatSkills.name: Radiant Blades
combatSkills.description: Holy blades appear and slashes enemies in a circle around Rei.

combatSkills.name: Divine Protection
combatSkills.description: A barrier appears and gives a defensive buff to Reis allies.

combatSkills.name: Holy Weapon
combatSkills.description: Holy energy gathers into Reis staff, forming a giant blade made of light.

characters.observations:
Holy Weapon can be casted up to three times, powering up the blade from LV1 to LV3. However, each level past the first one rapidly drains Reis life energy. Prolonged use of Holy Weapon LV3 is fatal.
She makes small dolls of her party members.
She doesnt drink alcohol at parties and feasts but is a lightweight if she does.
